# Git commits

When creating git commits in this repository:

- Do **not** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Co-authored-by: cursoragent`, or any Cursor/agent co-author trailer.
- Use only the human author's identity already configured in git (`user.name` / `user.email`).
- Never set commit author or committer to `cursoragent@cursor.com` or `Cursor`.

This keeps the GitHub contributors list accurate and avoids listing Cursor as a project contributor.
